headline: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) Declares Quarterly Dividends Including $0.21 Per Share On Common Stock
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) recently affirmed a cash dividend of $0.205 per share on its common shares, coupled with a declaration of preferred dividends, which may have modestly supported its 18% price increase last month. The company's impressive quarterly earnings, with net income rising from USD 219 million to USD 405 million, likely bolstered investor confidence.
